<i>Latest bulletins!</i>

<br>

<font style="font-size: 8px">20 September 2009</font>

<p>

<font color=#ff0000><i>MBBS 2009 is history!</i></font> 

<p>

<table width=400><tr><td>

<center>

Thanks to 

<a href=2009participants.html>all</a> who submitted their reports!

<p>

We have one last task! &nbsp; <i>Please check our data</i> on the web site 

<br>

and send any corrections or suggestions to

<a href="mailto:rhwiley@email.unc.edu">me</a>.

<p>

Before long, I plan to have some <i>statistical analysis</i> of trends to 
report.

<p>

Next March or April, we will plan a meeting of MBBS participants

<br>

and any others interested in our project

<br>

for assessment of our progress and recommitment for those who 
want to continue.

<br>

As always, some of our routes will be open for new participants.  

<br>

<i>Keep an eye out for recruits!</i>

</center>

